Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:13.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:17.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:20.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:22.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a pirate alliance\Nwith Trafalgar Law{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and have come to Dressrosa\Nto hand Caesar over to Doflamingo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When Luffy found out that the prize
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:46.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,for a fighting event was the Flare-Flare \NFruit, he decided to enter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's worth 77 million berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A member of the Straw \NHats! "Black Foot" Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's cut his head off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:04:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sanji was saved by Violet who \Nwas working for Doflamingo,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.62,0:04:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and has found out some shocking news!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.55,0:04:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the moment\Nyou all arrived here with Caesar,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you were walking into that man's trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you see is Dressrosa this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! It's time finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the list in the Colosseum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You entered the competition as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI told you not to!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it! I'll win it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldier-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.57,0:04:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... Hey, can we live together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A warrior who cries easily can't win\Na competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anesthetic flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meanwhile, after passing out \Nin the forest of Green Bit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Robin woke up in the Tontatta Kingdom -\Nthe country of the Little People.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.66,0:05:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Big Human is waking up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to run! Stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body is pinned to the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use trying to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a villainous Big Human, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is you Little People's kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's two fifty-seven.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We don't have time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Stratagem of the Century!\NDoflamingo Makes His Move!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:05.04,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,GREEN BIT - THE BEACH ON THE SOUTHEAST SIDE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The appointed time\Nfor Caesar's hand-over is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...in two minutes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clank!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, Law! This is Sanji!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Foot-{\i1}ya{\i0}! Did you find the factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not important now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is! "Black Foot" Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let the traitor \NViolet get away, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Kill them!\N--This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You assholes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what you're in for\Nif you hit Violet-{\i1}chan{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You've got to get out of there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI have to hand Caesar over soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo didn't resign\Nfrom the Seven Warlords!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if you hand Caesar over to him,\Nthere is no trade whatsoever!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.41,0:08:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.79,0:08:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...totally deceived!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Your Majesty!\N--Please don't quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Doflamingo-{\i1}sama{\i0}!\N--We need your explanation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.53,0:08:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you abdicate from the throne?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How noisy. Aren't they here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.85,0:09:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A warship is arriving into the harbor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen that logo before!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cipher Pol Aigis Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the Government officials\Nwho work directly under the World Nobles!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, people of Dressrosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the report on
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NDoflamingo's abdication from the throne
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Seven Warlords that\Nspread all over the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,0:09:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a mistake. Just a false report.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.34,0:10:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo-{\i1}sama{\i0} is not quitting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.68,0:10:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we will let the world know about it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,through an extra edition\Nof the newspaper at three today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.21,0:10:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be a secret until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NYou mustn't tell anybody about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All nations, keep living peacefully\Nas if nothing has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't a dream, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all happened for real\Nright before you people
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,came to this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it! I'm so confused!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.32,0:10:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The World Government?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's beyond a Warlord's control, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.61,0:11:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,scared of Doflamingo so I can't go
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but maybe you people can get away in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Leave the island now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The news about Doflamingo was a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that, Saka-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying the Navy Headquarters \Nwere fooled by a false report?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, it's so aggravating!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.36,0:11:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to go talk to\Nthe Five Elders at Marie Jois.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry but that's what happened.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need you to keep going ahead to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:05.29,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Trafalgar Law and Doflamingo's \Nrendezvous point.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All units! Go to the beach \Non the southeast side!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hurry up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool. It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy, too! I'm gonna hang up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clank!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are! Go after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nico Robin's upper half came out of the sand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nico-{\i1}ya{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a clone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was listening to the conversation.\NIt was Sanji, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are your actual body and Nose-{\i1}ya{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If what Black Foot-{\i1}ya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was talking about is true,\Nthe deal with Doflamingo is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:12:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what's gonna happen to my hand-over?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.58,0:13:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not gonna happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nico-{\i1}ya{\i0}! Summon Nose-{\i1}ya{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NLet's get off of the island now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, we're \Nunderground Green Bit now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Underground?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had some trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But both Usopp and I are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't help you but
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you're gonna escape,\Ngo without us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go to the harbor\Nwhere we agreed to meet up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.98,0:13:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are Trafalgar Law-{\i1}san{\i0}, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the new admiral,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujitora, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck to you guys, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.76,0:13:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joker!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.73,0:14:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect to see a Navy admiral here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm no longer a Warlord,\NI'm scared as hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.36,0:15:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, all competitors of\NBlock C are out there finally!¬Å
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,139 warriors!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a battle royal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna win this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the battle is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you're already\Nin the ring, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.25,0:15:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in Block D, aren't you, Cavendish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to break in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:15:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! Or you'll get eliminated!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.31,0:16:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.78,0:16:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kick his ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna drop every single \None of you into the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.99,0:16:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to get crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a big hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you get there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's arm stretched like rubber!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Devil Fruit eater?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A guy with the "Gum" power -\Nmust be Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.70,0:17:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna fight you next!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a normal punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.13,0:17:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not Lucy! He's Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.52,0:17:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?!\N--He did it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.81,0:18:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a normal kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain in the butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that guy with a helmet is interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen him before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, he's Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.26,0:18:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to the bleachers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.03,0:18:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! What are you doing?! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.31,0:18:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That little one is quite strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take care of him first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.69,0:18:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they're coming all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.09,0:19:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.26,0:19:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm a rubber man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:19:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's quite a fighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.01,0:20:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On this day,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the story spread by the News Coos
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:19.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Ntakes the whole world by surprise again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An extra edition?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like a correction about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.42,0:20:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:40.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A CANDIDATE FOR WARLORD
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.99,0:20:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The big news about Doflamingo was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mistake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's insane!\N--How could this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You used the authority of the
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.73,0:21:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,World Government\Nto fool the whole world...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.32,0:21:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...just to deceive 10 or so of us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.15,0:21:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Often, the more spectacular the magic,\Nthe simpler the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.30,0:21:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.11,0:21:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"That's ridiculous."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People usually have a stereotypical idea
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.02,0:21:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or an assumption like that\Nand that's what creates a blind spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.61,0:21:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can really do such a thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.73,0:21:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Neven if he hatched some scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.52,0:22:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.70,0:22:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're a Warlord and a king,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.99,0:22:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you don't have the power to spread a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.83,0:22:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nall over the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.37,0:22:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only people in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.34,0:22:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who have the power to do such \Na ridiculous thing are...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.46,0:22:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Celestial Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.34,0:22:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know Joker's past.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.06,0:22:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that will cost you your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.39,0:22:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.69,0:22:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.03,0:22:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's bit more complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.31,0:23:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have only one purpose, Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.69,0:23:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.71,0:23:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...wanted to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.96,0:23:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
